				<p class=""> V&eacute;ase <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rom/1.11-12?lang=spa#10" target="_blank">Romanos 1:11–12</a>.</p>
			</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote10-96991_002_006"><a name="-96991_002_006">&nbsp;</a>
